  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Frontend Developer (WFH)",
  "description": "<h3>Job Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Lead frontend technology selection, define frontend architecture standards, and continuously enhance shared/common components.</p></li><li><p>Design and develop the web frontend presentation layer and ensure seamless integration with backend services.</p></li><li><p>Optimize frontend performance and user experience, and resolve cross-browser and cross-platform compatibility issues.</p></li><li><p>Prepare technical and product documentation, conduct code reviews, and write unit tests to ensure code quality and project delivery.</p></li><li><p>Research and evaluate emerging frontend technologies, frameworks, and tools, introducing improvements where appropriate.</p></li><li><p>Ensure frontend applications are scalable, maintainable, and aligned with best practices.</p></li></ul><h3>Job Requirements</h3><ul><li><p><strong>At least 3 years</strong> of hands-on frontend development experience.</p></li><li><p>Strong proficiency in core frontend technologies:<br /><strong>JavaScript (ES6+), HTML5, CSS3</strong></p></li><li><p>Solid understanding of web standards, semantics, and separation of presentation and data.</p></li><li><p>Experience with modern frontend frameworks and libraries, especially <strong>Vue.js</strong> (Redux experience is a plus).</p></li><li><p>Familiar with CSS preprocessors such as <strong>Less or Sass</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience with build tools such as <strong>Webpack</strong> and <strong>Vite</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Good understanding of frontend engineering practices, modular development, and component-based architecture.</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with <strong>Node.js</strong>, with basic experience building services using frameworks such as <strong>Express or Koa</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Strong teamwork and communication skills, with the ability to contribute technically and improve overall team efficiency.</p></li><li><p>Passion for technology, strong learning ability, and a proactive, self-driven mindset.</p><p>Business Edge Personnel Services Singapore </p><p>EA License No: 96C4864 </p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R26159908 (Tan Ying Ying)</p></li></ul>",
